{"tid":1341894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好好学习毛主席十六字真言","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:04:21.000Z","uid":29836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e098d85a508496d901713191b7d25385b1970b76","tid":1341894,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"敌进我退，敌驻我扰，敌疲我打，敌退我追<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為在戰爭初期，敵強我弱的情況下，要以游擊戰和運動戰為主，通過犧牲中國部分大城市、重要幹線，贏得戰爭力量積蓄的時間和空間，同時通過游擊戰和運動戰來集中兵力和速戰速決&mdash;爭取對於敵人進行局部的殲滅和消耗，通過建立游擊根據地和游擊區來對敵人實施反包圍，通過積累小勝為最後的戰略反攻做準備。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/history/xpxqprq.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhistory%2Fxpxqprq.html&d=YI7gf4cr217w6pzPHhIkRWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=168736ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/history/xpxqprq.html</a><br />\n毛主席革命專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991566745468b0d7a1e63fc38db2c6157f39aba2","tid":1341894,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}